          <text>
                    <body>
                              <p>
                                        <addressee>Reverend Mr Leeser</addressee>
                              </p>
                              <p>I have taken up my Pen to inform you,<lb/> what the remnant of
                                                  <placeName>Israel</placeName> are doing<lb/> for
                                        South, namely in the State of
                                        <placeName>Texas</placeName><lb/> There are not many in the
                                        State, but still<lb/> you will find a sprinkling of them in
                                        every<lb/> village, some are adhering to our faith,
                                        others<lb/> again are intermarrying with
                                        (<add>גויים</add>)</p>
                              <p>I must not <sic>ommit</sic> to mention, what happened<lb/> in our
                                        city, a <persName>Mr E. Cohen</persName> lately from
                                                  <placeName>England</placeName><lb/> whose wife was
                                                  <sic>delievered</sic> of a Boy, with an<lb/>
                                        indomatible courage, he concluded at once<lb/> to perform
                                                  <sic>circumciesion</sic> himself, as we have<lb/>
                                        no (<add>מויעל</add>) nearer than <placeName>New
                                                  Orleans</placeName>, he was<lb/> persuaded by some
                                        of our coreligionist, to wait<lb/> till the child could be
                                        taken to <placeName>New Orleans</placeName><lb/> or to send
                                        for a (<add>מויעל</add>) his reply was as our<lb/> father
                                                  <persName>Abraham</persName> has performed it on
                                        the <date>8th Day</date><lb/> why should he not do it, the
                                        child is<lb/> doing well, the ceremony was performed in<lb/>
                                        the presence of a Surgeon</p>
                              <p rend="align(right)">S</p>
                              <p>Truly yours</p>
                              <p>
                                        <persName role="author">M Suligson</persName>
                              </p>
                              <p>
                                        <placeName>Galveston</placeName>
                                        <date>November 1851</date>
                              </p>
                              <p><persName>Mr Leeser</persName> any Errors above, please correct
                                        it</p>
                              <p>my respects to <persName>Mr Hackenberg</persName></p>
